frames.caption: A man kneels in a dark forest, his face buried in his hands, under a large, glowing full moon. The trees around him are tall and shadowy, creating an eerie atmosphere.
frames.description: The scene takes place in a dense, dark forest at night, illuminated by the bright full moon. A man is the central focus, kneeling on the ground with a distressed posture, suggesting emotional turmoil.

frames.caption: A werewolf howls under a full moon in a dark forest. The creature's mouth is open wide, revealing sharp teeth, as it raises its arms in a dramatic pose. The moonlight casts an eerie glow over the scene, highlighting the werewolf's fur and muscular form.
frames.description: The scene depicts a werewolf in a forest at night, illuminated by a bright full moon. The creature is in a dynamic pose, suggesting transformation or a call to the wild.
